observations.recommendation:
9. We recommended that the Municipal Mayor and its key officials:


     a) Determine the purposes of the available cash in the bank and provide
        such information to the Local Development Council;
     b) Identify the programs and projects that are currently needed by  the
        Municipality for inclusion in the Annual Investment Plan;
     c) Re-appropriate any unexpended  balances  to  fund  newly  identified
        projects, and;
     d) Implement the said programs and projects immediately.

2.10  The audit recommendations of the Audit Team were well taken.
